Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.86,0:00:19.86,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{Sorted By time}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.86,0:00:21.46,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A strong heart and the power of deduction!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.46,0:00:23.14,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A sharp rhythm gets to the root of its true nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.60,0:00:26.66,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Today, on a dangerous bus, Haibara's not her usual self.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.16,0:00:28.71,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.71,0:00:30.21,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.41,0:00:32.38,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.68,0:02:00.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{Timeshift by -360 frames}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.68,0:02:05.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you see it? The happy look on the client's face as he left?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.98,0:02:09.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's got no idea he drank his last shot tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.07,0:02:13.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh, bro?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.99,0:02:15.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bro?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.95,0:02:22.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, so that diva's up next?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.45,0:02:27.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Every time I hear her sing,\Nit sends shivers down my spine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.17,0:02:30.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And she's good-looking too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.96,0:02:34.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's your type, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.77,0:02:46.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Two dry martinis.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.02,0:02:48.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Courtesy of the lady on the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.23,0:02:54.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll take it with my compliments.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.57,0:02:59.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is the meaning of all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.78,0:03:06.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm asking you what you're up to...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.83,0:03:12.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vermouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.80,0:03:16.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.88,0:03:18.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a joke, a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.34,0:03:21.26,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Vermouth
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.76,0:03:21.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't make such a scary face.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.18,0:03:31.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I saw you drooling over a certain someone,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.44,0:03:33.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and thought I'd tease you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.11,0:03:36.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What're you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.73,0:03:41.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If anybody sees a famous actress like you talking to the likes of us...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.07,0:03:43.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.66,0:03:47.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Every eye's focused on that singer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.66,0:03:49.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Never mind that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.08,0:03:53.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have you found what you were looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.29,0:03:57.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I haven't located my primary target yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.92,0:03:59.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Target?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.21,0:04:03.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it time you told us what you're up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.34,0:04:05.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Give it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.97,0:04:10.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her ridiculous secret life is nothing new.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.52,0:04:13.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's a nice thing to say...{/sarcasm}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.06,0:04:16.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"A secret makes a woman woman."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.61,0:04:22.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's that touch of mystery that gives a woman her allure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.87,0:04:26.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You make me sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.53,0:04:31.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Never mind me, what about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.96,0:04:35.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you find that kitten that got away from you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.71,0:04:36.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.59,0:04:39.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it won't be long before I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.09,0:04:44.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My nose can sniff out traitors wherever they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.30,0:04:49.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And when I do, I'll show them what real fear is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.77,0:04:53.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her, and that man she's with.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.97,0:05:28.55,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Next stop is Beika Town, Third Street,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.55,0:05:31.06,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}in front of the Kodama Products main building.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.06,0:05:33.60,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Next stop is Beika Town, Third Street,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.60,0:05:36.14,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}in front of the Kodama Products main building.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.91,0:05:59.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You sure you can go skiing like this, Doc?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.17,0:06:01.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It serves him right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.55,0:06:04.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told him to stop because he'd catch cold,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.30,0:06:10.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but he was up all night image-training with a how-to-ski video.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.47,0:06:12.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I had no choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.93,0:06:17.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm in charge of you children! It's my duty to set an example.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.60,0:06:21.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But once we get there, you'd better rest at the lodge!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.36,0:06:25.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You need to take care of that cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.99,0:06:28.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't go out and play in the snow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.37,0:06:36.37,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Who's the child here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.37,0:06:39.83,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Next stop is in front of Beika Park.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.38,0:06:42.71,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Next stop is in front of Beika Park.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.95,0:07:17.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! More passengers are getting on! Take your seats.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.21,0:07:19.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.25,0:07:25.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You look bored to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.88,0:07:29.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like you're sad because you won't be seeing {\i1}her{\i0} for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.59,0:07:32.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or perhaps...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.43,0:07:36.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...you're sad because you won't be seeing {\i1}them{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.98,0:07:39.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're nuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.27,0:07:42.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These passengers have nothing to do with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.52,0:07:45.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who'd want to run into those guys on a cramped bus like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.69,0:07:47.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,especially with the kids on board?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.41,0:07:52.70,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}One of the men in black?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.20,0:07:54.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.41,0:07:58.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can sniff them out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.12,0:08:02.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone in the organization gives off a stench...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.33,0:08:07.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't notice any weird scent coming from you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.17,0:08:09.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would you cut that out?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.05,0:08:14.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if you've got a sixth sense like that,\Nthen the case with Pisco...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.47,0:08:18.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I had my suspicions.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.77,0:08:21.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then why didn't you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.39,0:08:24.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wasn't sure about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.06,0:08:27.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I sensed another presence too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.77,0:08:30.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Somebody far worse than Pisco.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.57,0:08:34.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A diabolical aura that chilled me to the bone...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.29,0:08:46.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kudo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...\NSwitch seats with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.71,0:08:48.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hide me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.21,0:08:50.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.09,0:08:52.05,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Haibara...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.01,0:08:55.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Araide{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.18,0:08:59.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh? You're all riding?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.97,0:09:03.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the check-up the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.06,0:09:03.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.48,0:09:07.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's wrong with Araide{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.56,0:09:11.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, you weren't at school when he dropped by for our check-ups, were you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.61,0:09:14.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you on a date today?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.74,0:09:19.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, no. She's a teacher at Teitan High, where I work.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.08,0:09:22.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hi, boys and girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.08,0:09:26.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Cool Kid! So, we meet again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.83,0:09:28.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know her?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.38,0:09:33.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, she's an English teacher at Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}'s school.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.22,0:09:37.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My name is Jodie Saintemillion.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.47,0:09:41.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm on a date with Dr. Araide today to Ueno Art Museum.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.97,0:09:45.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nah, we just happened to run into each other at the bus stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.02,0:09:49.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, shame on you embarrassing a lady like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.48,0:09:53.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you don't want weird rumors going around school, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.19,0:09:55.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh... yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.53,0:09:58.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That would be a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.23,0:10:29.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.69,0:10:35.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those two guys already have their ski gear on!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.36,0:10:37.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Guess they can't wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.15,0:10:40.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I can understand how they feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.37,0:10:41.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Same here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.20,0:10:50.38,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Geez. They've even got their goggles on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.55,0:10:55.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why don't we change too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.38,0:10:57.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.05,0:10:59.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We sent our bags on ahead of us, didn't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.34,0:11:01.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.39,0:11:03.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, you're so forgetful!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.85,0:11:09.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nobody move!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.31,0:11:12.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Make a move and you're dead meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.69,0:11:14.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.49,0:11:20.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Them!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.29,0:11:35.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nobody move!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.67,0:11:38.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Make a move and you're dead meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.01,0:11:41.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.64,0:11:43.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're hijacking...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.43,0:11:46.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.64,0:11:48.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.65,0:11:54.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't you hear me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.03,0:11:58.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told you to shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.74,0:12:01.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.36,0:12:03.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.03,0:12:06.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First, close the front door.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.83,0:12:07.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.29,0:12:15.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, change the front sign to "Out of Service".
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.59,0:12:17.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,R-Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.88,0:12:23.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, let's get this bus moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.47,0:12:25.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just drive around the city!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.26,0:12:26.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,R-Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.81,0:12:29.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Move it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.45,0:12:43.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.49,0:12:47.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At the next red light, I want you to call your company!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.20,0:12:48.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,R-Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.29,0:12:55.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good, you're good little children.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.58,0:13:03.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, hand over all the cell phones you got.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.09,0:13:06.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't hide 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.68,0:13:09.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you don't hand them over, you'll never make a phone call again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.53,0:13:26.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is W707, Kobayashi! W707, Kobayashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.78,0:13:30.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.29,0:13:35.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've just taken over this bus!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.75,0:13:37.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We have only one request!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.25,0:13:40.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Free Kunio Yashima from prison!{need better ears but shouldn't this be Yajima? Manga does say Yashima though.}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.75,0:13:46.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tell the police we're going to kill one passenger every hour until that happens!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.76,0:13:49.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll get back in touch in twenty minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.80,0:13:51.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Make sure you've got everything ready by then!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.48,0:13:59.86,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Kunio Yashima...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.82,0:14:02.15,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Kunio Yashima?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.69,0:14:07.24,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He's the leader of a gang that bombed and robbed a jewellery store last month.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.87,0:14:11.95,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He was arrested back then,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.54,0:14:15.33,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}but his three partners are still on the run.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.62,0:14:19.29,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I think Yashima used to be a jewellery broker.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.63,0:14:21.50,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.09,0:14:25.09,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The other three must not know the black market.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.55,0:14:30.35,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}They need their boss because he's the only one who can price the stolen jewellery.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.43,0:14:36.06,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Or maybe he's the only one who knows where the jewels are hidden...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.06,0:14:38.27,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and they're trying to get him out of jail so they can get to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.85,0:14:41.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.48,0:14:42.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hand it over!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.98,0:14:44.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah... I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.03,0:14:48.45,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Shuichi Akai\NPassenger
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.44,0:14:48.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't carry a cell phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.32,0:14:50.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sheesh. What a dork.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.20,0:14:52.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, old man next to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.66,0:14:55.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that thing you got in your ear?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.41,0:14:58.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a hearing aid!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.71,0:15:02.13,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Yasuhiko Machida\NPassenger
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.54,0:15:00.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've been almost deaf since childhood!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.00,0:15:02.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-So...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.84,0:15:07.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you over there! Stop that chewing sound!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.42,0:15:10.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? I'm just chewing gum.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.84,0:15:15.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're all gonna get arrested anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.59,0:15:14.89,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Miharu Tomino\NPassenger
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.52,0:15:18.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You might as well give up and make a run for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.31,0:15:23.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,F-Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.36,0:15:25.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.19,0:15:29.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good, that's how you should've been from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.26,0:15:52.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the matter? Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.51,0:15:54.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.72,0:15:57.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why, you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.39,0:16:00.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jodie...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.02,0:16:04.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.48,0:16:06.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, my God, what have I done?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.15,0:16:08.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.40,0:16:09.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't mean that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.86,0:16:12.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I always make a blunder and get clumsy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.28,0:16:13.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.70,0:16:15.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Forget it! Just sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.66,0:16:21.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's very, very exciting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.00,0:16:24.63,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Good grief. Is this teacher for real?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.13,0:16:33.09,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.47,0:16:35.30,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}while those guys are at the other end of the bus,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.22,0:16:40.93,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I'll use my earring-shaped phone to tell Inspector Megure about the situation...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.23,0:16:50.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What the hell are you doing,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.24,0:16:55.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you little {\i1}twerp{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.28,0:16:59.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, twerp...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.49,0:17:03.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you try anything funny again, you're really gonna get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.92,0:17:07.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oops, almost forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.67,0:17:09.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna hold on to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.63,0:17:12.17,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Damn! He took my phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.84,0:17:14.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.13,0:17:17.10,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But it's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.35,0:17:19.39,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He made a beeline for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.01,0:17:21.85,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}but he couldn't have seen what I was doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.10,0:17:24.85,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Which means...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.85,0:17:27.48,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}They've got an accomplice!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.44,0:17:32.24,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}One of the three people who can see me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.91,0:17:37.82,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But how did that person contact him,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.95,0:17:42.29,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and tell him what I was doing without letting anyone else know?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.29,0:17:45.04,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What method are they using?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.09,0:17:54.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sato here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.63,0:17:59.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The bus is currently heading for Takaido.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.26,0:18:02.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's travelling at about 50 km/h.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.60,0:18:04.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is Takagi at point E!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.60,0:18:07.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've caught sight of the bus!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.94,0:18:11.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are two suspects, both wearing ski gear!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.77,0:18:14.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't make out their faces under the hats and goggles,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.49,0:18:18.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but they seem to be armed with handguns.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.33,0:18:21.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What should we do, Inspector?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.33,0:18:24.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The bus may pass that way again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.33,0:18:26.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stay there until further notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.04,0:18:30.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dammit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.25,0:18:34.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If they're both armed, we can't take any chances.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.92,0:18:35.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.18,0:18:40.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've just received orders from the head office.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.89,0:18:44.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Our first priority is the safety of the hostages.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.56,0:18:51.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're to comply with the hijackers' demands and free Kunio Yashima.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.77,0:18:54.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Guess we've got no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.57,0:18:58.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's already been gunplay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.91,0:19:02.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And if they're members of Yashima's gang,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.53,0:19:05.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think at least one of them is an expert on explosives.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.66,0:19:11.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't imagine the devastation if they set off a bomb in the middle of town.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.08,0:19:14.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But we've got them trapped like rats.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.88,0:19:17.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The bus is going in circles around the city...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.09,0:19:21.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I bet they've got something up their sleeves.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.05,0:19:27.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Some plan that will let them escape right under our noses.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.39,0:19:32.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you've decided to comply, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.81,0:19:38.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tell Yashima to call us an hour after you've freed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.99,0:19:43.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Once we've confirmed from his own mouth that he's in a safe place,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.87,0:19:46.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,we'll start by freeing three hostages.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.91,0:19:49.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Got that? And don't try anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.55,0:20:02.84,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Two ski bags in a line...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.97,0:20:05.43,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It couldn't be...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.02,0:20:12.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.52,0:20:18.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you don't want your life,\NI'll grant your wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.73,0:20:20.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.57,0:20:21.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.20,0:20:28.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.79,0:20:30.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's just a little boy fooling around!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.58,0:20:34.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The police are complying with your demands!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.21,0:20:37.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have you considered that they might not be so cooperative...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.84,0:20:39.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,if you start shooting children?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.05,0:20:43.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-What was that, punk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.93,0:20:44.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.60,0:20:48.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What if you miss and shoot {\i1}that{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.98,0:20:53.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You two! Hurry up and get back to your seats!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.60,0:20:54.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.94,0:21:00.53,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}If he misses and shoots {\i1}that{\i0}?\NThat must mean those ski bags...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.28,0:21:02.61,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}are full of explosives!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.36,0:21:07.66,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I don't know what they're\Nplanning to use them for.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.16,0:21:11.08,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But one thing is clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.87,0:21:15.37,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}One of the three people behind me is in on it,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.37,0:21:17.25,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and is telling them about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.63,0:21:22.26,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I can't do anything until\NI figure out which one it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.30,0:21:24.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Haibara...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.59,0:21:26.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.55,0:21:28.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.97,0:21:32.23,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}W-What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.64,0:21:34.56,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I feel a piercing pressure...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.69,0:21:38.06,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}just like I felt back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.61,0:21:42.15,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's her... She's here, on this bus!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.90,0:21:45.66,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Did {\i1}they{\i0} send her? Are they after me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.61,0:21:47.78,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Or is it a coincidence...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.12,0:21:51.99,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}If my true identity is found out here...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.62,0:21:55.25,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and they figure out that I'm the one who betrayed the organization...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.46,0:21:58.67,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}then Dr. Agasa and everyone with me on the bus...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.17,0:21:59.92,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.29,0:22:02.09,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}every single person will be killed...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.46,0:22:04.72,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Of course, him too...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.63,0:22:06.72,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Without question...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.14,0:22:10.18,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.72,0:22:11.72,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Please...!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.39,0:22:13.72,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Don't let her find me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.78,0:23:47.99,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Wait, don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.32,0:23:50.53,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Someone's here?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.99,0:23:53.28,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}On this bus?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.95,0:23:55.20,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}One of {\i1}them{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.99,0:23:59.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right, when the bus comes out of the tunnel...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.21,0:24:01.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,it's game on!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.92,0:24:05.84,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I've always known there was no place for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.92,0:24:09.22,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I'm a fool, aren't I, sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.55,0:24:15.60,Signs,,0,0,0,,Next Conan:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.60,0:24:20.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint! Yes, yes!—Rearview Mirror
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.60,0:24:25.61,Signs,,0,0,0,,Look forward to the next episode!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.39,0:24:22.73,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,The movie {5}opens this Saturday!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.98,0:24:24.98,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Whatever the case, you're not getting in for free.
